an once' errors\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Agent failed to start! (出现次数:2), Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once (出现次数:2)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Stress test thread creation and execution - multiple stress threads (AdService--stress-17494638450 to 56) were created and running during the anomaly period\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Creating thread AdService--stress-17494638450, Starting thread AdService--stress-17494638450, Running thread AdService--stress-17494638450\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **明确的故障注入模式**：检测到Chaos Mesh的Byteman代理正在对adservice服务执行压力测试（stress test）\n2. **影响范围**：所有3个adservice实例（adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2）都受到影响\n3. **时间匹配**：异常时间段与压力测试执行时间完全吻合\n4. **错误模式**：包括代理启动失败、重复加载错误、压力线程执行异常等\n\n**建议**：这看起来是计划内的混沌工程测试，而非真正的系统故障。建议确认是否为预期的测试活动，并检查测试配置是否合理。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于对链路追踪数据的分析，我已经识别出系统在指定时间段内的异常情况。以下是初步扫描结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->AdService\",\n    \"frontend->CartService\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"广告服务响应时间异常增长：从正常5.4秒增加到45秒（8.3倍增长），影响所有frontend实例\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"购物车服务响应时间异常：GetCart从2.5秒增加到23.5秒，AddItem从5.2秒激增至134.8秒（25.8倍增长）\"\n    },\n    {\n      component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis访问延迟异常：HGET操作从1.5秒增加到12.4秒（8倍增长），可能影响购物车服务\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"物流服务响应时间异常：ShipOrder从228毫秒增加到881毫秒（3.9倍增长）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"EmailService\",\n      \"reason